lt, was Inklusion sein soll. Was bleibt, ist ein Einsatz für die Anerkennung der Kontingenz und Umstrittenheit pädagogischer Ordnungen.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aDiversity in the workplacezGermany. 0aEducationxSocial aspects. 0aInclusive educationzGermany. 0aMarginality, Social. 0aSocial integration. 4aBehinderung. 4aBildung. 4aBildungspolitik. 4aBildungstheorie. 4aDemokratie. 4aDemokratietheorie. 4aEthik. 4aGesellschaftsanalyse. 4aHegemonietheorie. 4aMacht. 4aPolitik. 4aPolitische Philosophie. 4aPädagogik. 4aRadikaldemokratie. 7aEDUCATION / Educational Policy & Reform / General.2bisacsh  aDemocracy.  aDisability Studies.  aEducation.  aEducational Policy.  aEthics.  aHegemony Theory.  aPedagogy.  aPolitical Philosophy.  aPolitics.  aPower.  aRadical Democracy.  aSocial Analyses.  aTheories of Democracy.  aTheory of Education.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2z978311069629508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Sociology, Education, Psychology 2020z9783110704549oZDB-23-SEW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2020z9783111025124oZDB-23-TGP0 cprintz978383765302140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839453025?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839453025423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839453025/original  a978-3-11-069629-5  DG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2b2020  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2020  aZDB-23-SEWb2020  aZDB-23-TGPb2020